    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1248">
<l>parintavar nalkāreṉ ṟēṅkip pirintavar </l>
<l>piṉcelvāy pētaiyeṉ ṉeñcu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You are a fool, O my soul! to go after my departed one, while you mourn that he is not kind enough to favour you.</l>
